-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">地沟油、塑化剂、非食品添加剂正在毒害国人的身体；明胶薯粉、致癌毒大米、硫磺熏制的土豆让我们无所适从；国人的肿瘤患病率高达22%，病从口入，非安全食品是主要原因，大家一起来关注食品的安全健康!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">东莞市钜川食品有限公司成立的宗旨是：把全世界绿色天然、物美价优、并经国际权威部门严格检测、符合中国标准的安全健康食品和饮品送到您的手中，在保证安全健康的同时，也让您入口难忘！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">东莞钜川食品有限公司的采购人员都是从香港聘请的食品行业资深人士，他们会在全世界了解品尝当地著名食品，选定产品后会亲自到有关工厂调研，了解每一个产品的每一个生产环节和包装环节。从工厂周边的环境，到生产加工的设备和资质；从上游原材料的生产贮存，到食品的制作包装；从食品在当地市场上的销售情况，再到该品牌的口碑等等都要经过严格考核。最后把样品拿回国内，经&ldquo;广东省出入境检验检疫局检验检疫技术中心&rdquo;检验合格，钜川食品有限公司才确定作为本公司选定的进口产品。在大货实际进口时，同样须经&ldquo;广东省出入境检验检疫局检验检疫技术中心&rdquo;重新检测合格后，才会放货进来，可以说是重重把关。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">如今，钜川食品有限公司首次引进印度尼西亚&ldquo;西莫尼（Cimory）&rdquo;品牌的常温酸奶（详见西莫尼品牌介绍）。公司两次派人到印尼西莫尼集团考察工厂和连锁美食购物游乐休闲中心，整洁的工厂坐落在青山绿水之间，生意火爆的连锁中心让人振撼，经过艰苦的谈判，钜川食品有限公司终于获得中国区唯一的品牌总代理权。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;</span></p>');
