; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">我们的团队：</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">我们团队的核心成员由具有丰富国内市场开拓经验的营销人士、食用糖研究开发方面的专家及食用糖生产经验丰富的管理人员组成，营销、生产和研发团队也在不断的发展壮大。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; font-weight: inherit; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" />\r\n我们的营销：</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 15px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; pad