INSERT INTO `destoon_company_data` VALUES('5024','<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; text-align: center;\">品牌故事</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 28px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">吉林省金塔实业（集团）股份有限公司，坐落于吉林省洮南市，占地面积32万平方米，成立于2004年8月，2010年10月完成股份制改造。注册资金1.5967亿元，总资产13.7亿元。主要生产以农业、食品和生物科技三大板块的上百种产品。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 28px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">在生物科技板块，建成总投资2.5亿元、占地面积4.5万平方米，包含色素生产车间、渣料处理车间、流体萃取车间等在内的、日投料120吨、目前国内单机投料规模最大的CO2超临界萃取辣椒红色素生产线；建成总投资3000万元，占地面积1000平方米，建筑面积1500平方米的功能红曲米生产线；建成总投资1.5亿元，占地面积7000平方米，技术领先的金塔清风肽碱性小分子生产线。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 28px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">集团先后通过了ISO9001:2008质量管理体系认证、ISO14001:2004环境管理体系认证、ISO22000:2005食品安全管理体系认证、良好农业规范认证、有机产品认证、犹太认证、BRC认证、生态原产地保护产品认证等。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 28px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">先后获得了&ldquo;农业产业化国家重点龙头企业&rdquo;、&ldquo;吉林省优秀出口企业质量安全奖&rdquo;、&ldquo;国家级出口食品农产品质量安全示范区&rdquo;、&ldquo;中国辣椒第一家&rdquo;、&ldquo;中国驰名商标&rdquo;、&ldquo;吉林省创新型科技企业&rdquo;、国家级&ldquo;守合同重信用企业&rdquo;、国家级&ldquo;出入境检验检疫信用管理AA级企业&rdquo;、&ldquo;中国质量诚信企业&rdquo;、&ldquo;全国文明单位&rdquo;、&ldquo;吉林省质量奖&rdquo;等殊荣。集团董事长杨茂义先后获得&ldquo;全国创业之星&rdquo;、&ldquo;全国青年创业致富带头人&rdquo;、&ldquo;全国道德模范提名奖&rdquo;、&ldquo;全国劳动模范&ldquo;等荣誉称号。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 28px; font-family: \'冬青黑体简体中文 W3\', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">金塔集团以&ldquo;提供健康产品、致力幸福生活&rdquo;为使命，贯彻&ldquo;以订单调控规模，以加工平衡市场，以创汇优化业绩，以诚信打造品牌&rdquo;的经营方针，借助资本市场的力量，未来五年，将在打造一大平台、实现两大目标、经营三大板块、实施四大支撑、达到五大效果的&ldquo;12345&rdquo;战略构思的指引下，积极践行战略部署，力争到2020年实现年销售收入30亿元，利税8亿元，开创集团发展史上新的辉煌篇章！</span></p>');
